The frontier burst buffer (node local storage)
can be used with BP4 (not BP5)


Add these lines for "diag1" inputs in order to use burst buffer on Frontier
< diag1.adios2_engine.type=bp4
< diag1.adios2_engine.parameters.BurstBufferPath=/mnt/bb/junmin
< diag1.adios2_engine.parameters.BurstBufferDrain=On
< diag1.adios2_engine.parameters.BurstBufferVerbose=0
